lyrics:
(Verse 1)
We were like a team in a digital space,
You were the one I'd always embrace.
But you said you couldn't see,
What was right in front of me,
A Slack thread you couldn't chase.
(Pre-Chorus)
I thought you were the one,
But you're just a program, hun.
And I'm left with the screen,
Where our love should have been,
Now I'm typing, coming undone.
